column5: Passives Reference:
* Empower Fire (lv X): Increases party Fire damage dealt by X%
* Empower Ice (lv X): Increases party Ice damage dealt by X%
* Empower Lightning (lv X): Increases party Lightning damage dealt by X%
* Empower Earth (lv X): Increases party Earth damage dealt by X%
* Empower Wind (lv X): Increases party Wind damage dealt by X%
* Empower Water (lv X): Increases party Water damage dealt by X%
* Empower Holy (lv X): Increases party Holy damage dealt by X%
* Empower Dark (lv X): Increases party Dark damage dealt by X%
* Empower Poison (lv X): Increases party Poison damage dealt by X%
* Dampen Fire (lv X): Reduces party Fire damage taken by X%
* Dampen Blizzard (lv X): Reduces party Ice damage taken by X%
* Dampen Lightning (lv X): Reduces party Lightning damage taken by X%
* Dampen Earth (lv X): Reduces party Earth damage taken by X%
* Dampen Air (lv X): Reduces party Wind damage taken by X%
* Dampen Water (lv X): Reduces party Water damage taken by X%
* Dampen Light (lv X): Reduces party Holy damage taken by X%
* Dampen Dark (lv X): Reduces party Dark damage taken by X%
* Dampen Poison (lv X): Reduces party Poison damage taken by X%
* Health Boon (lv X): Increases party max HP by X% of the magicites total max HP (100% main, 50% sub)
* Attack Boon (lv X): Increases party ATK by X% of the magicites total ATK (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers
* Defense Boon (lv X): Increases party DEF by X% of the magicites total DEF (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers
* Magic Boon (lv X): Increases party MAG by X% of the magicites total MAG (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers
* Resistance Boon (lv X): Increases party RES by X% of the magicites total RES (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers
* Mind Boon (lv X): Increases party MND by X% of the magicites total MND (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers
* Blade Ward (lv X): Reduces party physical damage taken from PHY or NAT attacks by X%
* Spell Ward (lv X): Reduces party magical damage taken from BLK, WHT, BLU, SUM or NAT attacks by X%
* Precise Strikes (lv X): Increases party critical chance by X% (additive with other critical chance modifiers)
* Deadly Strikes (lv X): Increases party critical damage by X% (additive with the default +50% and other critical damage modifiers)
* Fast Act (lv X): Increases party cast speed by X%
* Healing Boon (lv X): Increases all HP restored to the party by X%
* Healing Damper (lv X): Decreases all HP restored to the party by X%
* Hand of Vengeance (lv X): Increases party damage dealt by X*(1-HP%)^3 percent, where HP% is the character's current HP rate
* Surging Power (lv X): Increases party damage dealt by X*HP/10000 percent, where HP is the character's current amount of HP (max +X%, reached at 10000 HP)
* Damage Push (lv X): Increases party damage dealt by X%, acting and taking damage grants 25% less SB points
* Stat Boon (lv X): Increases party ATK, DEF, MAG, RES and MND by X% of the respective magicites total stats (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers

* Earth King's Blessing (lv X): Increases party Earth Damage dealt by X%, reduces party Earth damage taken by X%, increases party damage dealt to Titan by 10% and reduces party Earth damage taken from Titan by 10%, increases party damage dealt to White Odin by 30% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by 30%

* Thunderous Blessing (lv X): Increases party Lightning Damage dealt by X%, reduces party Lightning damage taken by X%, increases party damage dealt to Ramuh by 10% and reduces Lightning party damage taken from Ramuh by 10%, increases party damage dealt to White Odin by 30% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by 30%

* Imperial Blessing (lv X): Increases party Water Damage dealt by X%, reduces party Water damage taken by X%, increases party damage dealt to Leviathan by 10% and reduces Water party damage taken from Leviathan by 10%, increases party damage dealt to White Odin by 30% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by 30%

* Perdition's Blessing (lv X): Increases party Fire Damage dealt by X%, reduces party Fire damage taken by X%, increases party damage dealt to Ifrit by 10% and reduces Fire party damage taken from Ifrit by 10%, increases party damage dealt to White Odin by 30% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by 30%

* Hoarfrost Blessing (lv X): Increases party Ice Damage dealt by X%, reduces party Ice damage taken by X%, increases party damage dealt to Shiva by 10% and reduces Ice party damage taken from Shiva by 10%, increases party damage dealt to White Odin by 30% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by 30%

* Majestic Blessing (lv X): Increases party Wind Damage dealt by X%, reduces party Wind damage taken by X%, increases party damage dealt to Valefor by 10% and reduces Wind party damage taken from Valefor by 10%, increases party damage dealt to White Odin by 30% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by 30%

* Sanctified Blessing (lv X): Increases party Holy Damage dealt by X%, reduces party Holy damage taken by X%, increases party damage dealt to Alexander by 10% and reduces Holy party damage taken from Alexander by 10%, increases party damage dealt to White Odin by 30% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by 30%

* Gloomshade Blessing (lv X): Increases party Dark Damage dealt by X%, reduces party Dark damage taken by X%, increases party damage dealt to Diablos by 10% and reduces Dark party damage taken from Diablos by 10%, increases party damage dealt to White Odin by 30% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by 30%

* Poison Blessing (lv X): Increases party Poison Damage dealt by X%, reduces party Poison damage taken by X%, increases party damage dealt to White Odin by 30% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by 30%

* Argent Sage's Blessing (lv X): Increases party damage dealt to White Odin by X% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by X%, increases party ATK, DEF, MAG, RES and MND by X% of the respective magicites total stats (100% main, 50% sub), after modifiers

* Lord's Seal: Element (lv X): Increases matching element damage dealt by the party by X%, reduces matching element damage taken by the party by X%, increases party damage dealt to White Odin by 5% and reduces White Odin's current element damage party damage taken from White Odin by 5%
